1. git submodule init
2. git submodule update
3. mkdir build && cd build
4. cmake ../src
5. make (osx) or devenv (win32)

You've done it!  now bp-imagealter/build/ImageAlter contains the 
built service.  For your present directory you can run it:

now you're ready to run tests:

6. ../test/runtests.rb 
